notes.content:
- Always reach Todoist zero!
- No items in inbox at end of day
- Priorities for:
     1. Have to do - never move this task
     2. Should do - move tasks only if really necessary
     3. Want to do - may be moved if no more time available
     4. No Priority - used for reminders and unimportant tasks
- Quicky label for non-recurring items which take 15 minutes or less
- Every item needs a time! Otherwise they are lost todos and will never be done.
